window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Just outside Los Angeles, a prisoner hidden away for 70 years sits up, gets off the bed and disappears through a solid wall. </p> <p>In Australia, a magician impresses audiences by producing real elephants. Nobody realizes it's not an illusion. </p> <p>Across the world, individuals and ancient organizations with supernatural power suddenly detect the presence of something even they can't understand. </p> <p>At the center of it all, Seb Varden, a 32-year old musician with a secret in his past, slits his wrists, is shot dead and run over on the freeway. He's had better days. </p> <p>Seb is about to discover the universe is a far more complicated place than he'd ever imagined. </p>"; 
